his into the shared Google Calendar flow** because the **Google Calendar API is disabled** for this Gog project/account (`403 accessNotConfigured`).\\n- Item that should be added for `toledo970501@gmail.com` once Calendar API is enabled:\\n  - **“Complete and send Zoolatech coding challenge” — due today (2026-03-27), high priority**\\n\\nWhatsApp reminder to send externally:\\n- **Recipient:** `+573183718246`\\n- **Suggested concise message:**\\n  - `Pendiente hoy: terminar y enviar el Zoolatech coding challenge. Andrea lo mandó el 24-Mar y daba 1-2 días; con el contexto actual, vence hoy. También quedan pendientes el tema de acceso/despliegue en Vercel para tradelab-front y revisar las alertas de GitGuardian por secretos expuestos.`\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_091789ebac5481e50169c68061524c81919c5d321c53f29cda\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 1150,\n            \"output\": 536,\n            \"totalTokens\": 35094,\n            \"cacheRead\": 33408,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.019267\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774616658658,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_091789ebac5481e50169c6805573b481919ef80a99474b1e22\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"8e719779\",\n            \"seq\": 23\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:0e6263ae-c5c2-4bbf-a409-9b91e9d78db2\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"unknown\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: Recordatorio entrenamiento pecho 5AM\",\n      \"displayName\": \"Cron: Recordatorio entrenamiento pecho 5AM\",\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774605008034,\n      \"sessionId\": \"d88a8de5-1ffa-48ae-a0b3