se con Gustavo para armar la lista y ejecutar.\nComprar agua según tablero — PENDIENTE; aún no pregunté a Jorge por canal externo real; próximo paso: enviarle el mensaje por WhatsApp ahora."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":90,"totalTokens":19882,"cacheRead":3369,"cacheWrite":16420,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774570008888,"responseId":"msg_01TMqvrfFDg8Ksd7b3uPg9Fs","__openclaw":{"id":"642fdf84","seq":69}}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:ca097918-7155-44b5-80f9-4408f88c50ef","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Atlas OS review - midday","displayName":"Cron: Atlas OS review - midday","updatedAt":1774630800014,"sessionId":"a53c02bb-082b-4f2a-930c-f7630dfa1c70","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":57136,"estimatedCostUsd":1.2783175,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\a53c02bb-082b-4f2a-930c-f7630dfa1c70.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":""},{"type":"text","text":"Para WhatsApp a +573183718246\n\nRevisé completo el Tasks Tracker y lo dejé más honesto contra la realidad.\n\nQué moví:\n- Entrenamiento torso - Viernes 27 marzo 5:00 AM (Ares) → Done\n  - Sí había evidencia real de entrega: la rutina ya fue enviada al grupo Smart Project el 26-Mar 5:00 PM. No la dejé “en progreso” porque ya hubo salida real.\n- Definir sesión de entrenamiento siguiente (Ares) → Blocked\n  - Intenté coordinar a Ares otra vez y no devolvió respuesta útil. El bloqueo sigue siendo técnico/routing (Ollama qwen3:30b + timeouts).\n- Comprar mercado (Hestia) → Waiting\n  - El estado real es que no se ejecutó y depende de confirmar faltantes con Gustavo.\n- Comprar agua según tablero (Hestia) → Blocked\n  - No hay confirmación real de que Hestia haya contactado a Jorge; además no respondió en esta revisión.\n- Ideas de viaje para la siguiente semana (Atlas) → Waiting\n  - Ya no está “in progress” de verdad: las opciones ya existen y ahora depende de decisión de Gustavo.\n- Tarea nueva “Recuérdame que no te he respondido…” → sigue Backlog\n  - La dejé explícitamente como tarea sin owner claro.\n\nQué coordiné:\n- Le exigí a Ares estado real, primer paso o bloqueo explícito.\n- Le exigí a Hestia estado real, primer paso o bloqueo explícito.\n- Ninguno respondió de forma útil dentro de esta revisión, así que escalé actualizando el tracker según evidencia real, no por intención.\n\nQué quedó bloqueado:\n- Resumen del challenge ZooLATECH → sigue Blocked por falta de acceso efectivo al adjunto/correo dentro de este flujo.\n- Definir sesión de entrenamiento siguiente → Blocked por Ares inestable/no operativo de forma confiable.\n- Comprar agua según tablero → Blocked por falta de ejecución/confirmación real de Hestia.\n\nQué sigue:\n1. Reactivar o rerutear a Ares a un modelo estable para destrabar entrenamiento.\n2. Confirmar con Gustavo faltantes base si se quiere mover “Comprar mercado”.\n3. Asignar owner real a la tarea del recordatorio por WhatsApp.\n4. Si se abre acceso al correo/adjunto, retomar ZooLATECH de inmediato.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_089fb536a0185fbd0169c6b8573878819195b9e7d886f0b12d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":57136,"output":535,"totalTokens":57671,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.15086500000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774630990413,"responseId":"resp_089fb536a0185fbd0169c6b852c1ac819181ffe8c6ec9a834c","__openclaw":{"id":"6cf1e045","seq":21}}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:b824f7b0-7497-4984-b0ff-d1bd45539f3c","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: daily-email-review-and-whatsapp-reminder","displayName":"Cron: daily-email-review-and-whatsapp-reminder","updatedAt":1774616555303,"sessionId":"a3b8b3c9-4278-456f-ab89-f1258efbf7bc","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":34558,"estimatedCostUsd":0.29850150000000003,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\a3b8b3c9-4278-456f-ab89-f1258efbf7bc.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":""},{"type":"text","text":"Inbox review done for `atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com`.\n\nRelevant items found:\n- **URGENTE: Zoolatech coding challenge** — forwarded by Gustavo on **2026-03-25 20:31** from Andrea Martínez (`amartinez@zoolatech.com`).\n  - Original mail says the challenge was sent on **2026-03-24 14:52**.\n  - Andrea said he had **1–2 days** to complete it and it usually takes **1–2 hours**.\n  - With the provided context (“3 days from 2026-03-24”), this is effectively **due today, Friday 2026-03-27**.\n- **Pending but not hard-deadline today:**\n  - GitHub PR notification for `gtolbar/tradelab-front` about a **Vercel deployment access issue**.\n  - GitGuardian alerts about **exposed secrets** in `atlasiaagente-alt/openclaw-assistant`.\n  - GitHub repo invite from Gustavo to `gtolbar/tradelab-front` still appears pending.\n- **No other clear today-specific forwarded tasks or near-term deadlines** showed up in the inbox review. The rest was mostly Notion promotional/onboarding mail.\n\nCalendar flow:\n- I **could not organize/schedule this into the shared Google Calendar flow** because the **Google Calendar API is disabled** for this Gog project/account (`403 accessNotConfigured`).\n- Item that should be added for `toledo970501@gmail.com` once Calendar API is enabled:\n  - **“Complete and send Zoolatech coding challenge” — due today (2026-03-27), high priority**\n\nWhatsApp reminder to send externally:\n- **Recipient:** `+573183718246`\n- **Suggested concise message:**\n  - `Pendiente hoy: terminar y enviar el Zoolatech coding challenge. Andrea lo mandó el 24-Mar y daba 1-2 días; con el contexto actual, vence hoy. También quedan pendientes el tema de acceso/despliegue en Vercel para tradelab-front y revisar las alertas de GitGuardian por secretos expuestos.`","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_091789ebac5481e50169c68061524c81919c5d321c53f29cda\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1150,"output":536,"totalTokens":35094,"cacheRead":33408,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.019267}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774616658658,"responseId":"resp_091789ebac5481e50169c6805573b481919ef80a99474b1e22","__openclaw":{"id":"8e719779","seq":23}}]},{"key":"agent:main:cron:0e6263ae-c5c2-4bbf-a409-9b91e9d78db2","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Recordatorio entrenamiento pecho 5AM","displayName":"Cron: Recordatorio entrenamiento pecho 5AM","updatedAt":1774605008034,"sessionId":"d88a8de5-1ffa-48ae-a0b3-3a5f3d363710","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":200000,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"failed","startedAt":1774605000959,"endedAt":1774605008027,"runtimeMs":7068,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\d88a8de5-1ffa-48ae-a0b3-3a5f3d363710.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1774605046872,"errorMessage":"Connection error.","__openclaw":{"id":"0d1d62e0","seq":8}},{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1774605052391,"errorMessage":"Connection error.","__openclaw":{"id":"3af1f021","seq":9}}]},{"key":"agent:ares:cron:95070b27-20b2-4ee5-b54f-c4e18195892c","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Recordatorio gym torso 5AM","displayName":"Cron: Recordatorio gym torso 5AM","updatedAt":1774604402399,"session