{"type":"message","id":"d6cc3980","parentId":"fe6d6904","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:00:33.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Clarifying task management**\n\nI’m wondering if we can skip self-coordination, but it seems like the first step needs a clear decision. It’s about explicitly blocking it and updating our notion accordingly. For the Seguros reminder, maybe we should label it as \"Waiting\" or \"Done\" since it’s a recurring backlog item. I’ll need to check if the cron job exists and consider listing the jobs we have. I think querying relevant jobs will help clarify this!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_075ff92e4d0e9e660169c7d0e7c7988191b1ebced0e9f1ffb3\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpx9Dx-Vdrc1g-B3c4sn2yH5hLRaBZjS-HYKdgmxtCLj8-4XMjg2Ameo1yURsRuFecB11JVPrZbs7-gQuyvjrBUtEv-JVya9Gt74dOrOTsHfuBuX_WKRpvPyZ_OivMlcEfUmFdbo2t8CsGEQyjHPCI5Ppo_AshM6QdOYC-8S20m7H51_IShcTLjnF-vmA3tP6zOY5JQLLp3eZ3D7Re2uWwYE3CDoOdQcKaXx9VwD6FG_QM6dNVRizi1JQw8jtMuEbiT1YMFwelE439f7at6M6ltBodgcE4FvEIEuaPDOa8V8g7ewovFj656LVr-7VX72cif8ZWpeFYUbdj54_jxqWQ2zTF14tRs9ZpXvMiV6yWP00hmkE08ezS6CBYT-l5W2L0ZeE8CcDM10t-_eYZxuKTOsqOnK-9DlgHFNA14FKqY-nKp3MOi_eT-drEA8LY7R7JyyTUc-kTSGmYXznpm_nUMsQ5q8pUH6pQJhqt1W0fCRlPzNxsqF1lGftCQlWYn4TMuilDQ_qlId1Dek-amd_3mTtyKymeGGMV_jkwVpv6vIF7AWtZ7MUuNKRv52a-9QkVNTxhVku2mrQHOJ-M7wqWub8Ql_Ym_B3Y4loRBM__D8s3Y4f7C2uvYbZUL9TWn5W1RLdHNeSG3p6z5864NsvJ-62Mq07zMw4sUvLK14N9cirGJgVqPFhY3V4YR9vhN4dsNoOAV_aB9BxyBqdItuHqw-e1I3RYei1hlvKj4SvmdpNqk4YliMCEqaY06w2eifJfHz31LFRUW_Qnrqh8LkEDaNXnWwQEVcCW6aQ-JHRNgmTnX9TLyd1Rf3xPdcd1pZBGV0ZtzGiGwJtLPAxa1WTUZWdEAj_aZ6ZhQLLHcTs5bpdaOqRJPmpiTSF8JTscgfc_o2sPIZLRwUj0y8vZpo8l47iG1QhhwfU-YTijquZeGFDvdLklgEaH14XcAxF1qe9YTvijW_uaTGDyUhRmO54FPDF5iHiyg9qYgzomjyroz1Muy1Rk_vWtyfqqtIJqXFC9OSkxD_5e7aPv68KxMyGJNwAtUv_vMvhye4zBX9r9KNoy87TNM6lBpj26aSFi2MUbuxo3Ip8H1kPUjB4UY3sYpeK21zCwHKYO_JnOpxCyj1mYeb9-8SZrvOHUDO-VFkkRbD2aZr-RFP3HrghdBtlBNEscIdk3u0oa_Pz_jBIlhMoYdJiqVBJvX9Ro2jcxQklfdZK06cuupzh0m