arify this!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Solo había dos tareas activas en Backlog/Next con dueño claro hoy, ambas de Atlas. Voy a validar su estado real y ajustar el tracker para que quede honesto.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_075ff92e4d0e9e660169c7d0f1d1148191ba8fa7d2eace569a\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_sG9wSnNOh0gZ81qGB8SkU6Zw|fc_075ff92e4d0e9e660169c7d0f1f51c8191895eb6fbb02a6992","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\ops\\invoice-system-plan.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\ops\\\\invoice-system-plan.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_RUSz2k9sJOpTnItLTwwFDWeL|fc_075ff92e4d0e9e660169c7d0f1f52c8191a4e383a1ce2196dc","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true},"partialJson":"{\"action\":\"list\",\"includeDisabled\":true}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":19341,"output":393,"cacheRead":30464,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50198,"cost":{"input":0.04835250000000001,"output":0.005895,"cacheRead":0.0076159999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0618635}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774702818874,"responseId":"resp_075ff92e4d0e9e660169c7d0e3f9fc8191ad721fe8ed0238b6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ac37895","parentId":"d6cc3980","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:00:33.508Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_sG9wSnNOh0gZ81qGB8SkU6Zw|fc_075ff92e4d0e9e660169c7d0f1f51c8191895eb6fbb02a6992","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Sistema base — factura mensual al proveedor\n\nFecha: 2026-03-27\n\n## Objetivo\nDejar listo el esqueleto para que, cuando Gustavo comparta la plantilla, se pueda:\n1. recordar a tiempo\n2. calcular horas/valor base\n3. prearmar borrador\n\n## Reglas conocidas\n- Zona horaria: Colombia\n- Días laborables: lunes a viernes\n- Festivos colombianos: no se trabajan\n- Jornada: 8 horas/día\n- Tarifa recordada: **USD 38/hora**\n\n## Cálculo base provisional\n- Valor diario: **USD 304**\n- Fórmula mensual provisional:\n  - `días hábiles trabajados x 8 x 38`\n\n## Pendientes para automatizar bien\n- Plantilla real de factura\n- Confirmar si la tarifa sigue siendo exactamente USD 38/hora\n- Definir formato de salida (PDF, DOCX, Google Docs, Notion, etc.)\n- Definir si hay campos variables: número de factura, NIT, razón social, fechas de corte, impuestos, moneda final\n\n## Siguiente paso concreto\nCuando llegue la plantilla:\n- mapear campos\n- crear checklist de llenado\n- dejar un borrador reusable\n\n## Idea de automatización posterior\n- Recordatorio **3 a 5 días antes de fin de mes**\n- Si existe plantilla estructurada, prearmar borrador automático con:\n  - mes\n  - rango de fechas\n  - días laborables\n  - horas\n  - subtotal\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774702833506}}
{"type":"message","id":"795ffc86","parentId":"7ac37895","timestamp":"2026-03-28T13:00:33.510Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_RUSz2k9sJOpTnItLTwwFDWeL|fc_075ff92e4d0e9e660169c7d0f1f52c8191a4e383a1ce2196dc","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"03b29602-b584-4ec0-9241-b0d74393cc82\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Atlas OS review - morning\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774388052968,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774616555300,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Revisa el Tasks Tracker de Notion (DB id: 32f0a0b1-97cc-81a8-9443-df3f85f2ffc7, dentro de la página 'Atlas OS - Home' id: 32f0a0b1-97cc-8115-9e62-ec8765ad533c) y úsalo como dashboard operativo. Flujo obligatorio: (1) Lee todas las tareas del tracker; (2) por cada tarea con estado Backlog o Next y dueño claro, coordina activamente al agente responsable (Prometeo, Ares, Hestia o Atlas); (3) exige decisión, primer paso concreto o bloqueo explícito; (4) si un subagente no responde o queda ambiguo, destrábalo o escálalo; (5) actualiza el estado en el tracker según resultado real: usa siempre Backlog, Next, In progress, Waiting, Blocked o Done; (6) nunca marques Done sin confirmación real de entrega; (7) al final envía a WhatsApp +573183718246 un resumen breve: qué moviste, qué coordinaste, qué quedó bloqueado y qué sigue.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 1800\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"to\": \"+573183718246\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774702800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774616400007,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 155293,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1774702800006\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b824f7b0-7497-4984-b0ff-d1bd45539f3c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-email-review-and-whatsapp-reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774390465819,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774616679301,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Review the Gmail inbox of atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com using gog. Look for forwarded messages from Gustavo's personal email, pending items for today, and near-term deadlines. Organize the relevant items into the appropriate shared calendar flow for Gustavo by citing/scheduling what applies toward toledo970501@gmail.com, then send Gustavo a concise WhatsApp reminder to +573183718246 with what he has pending today and any nearby deadlines. Include important context if relevant. Example current context: he has 3 days from 2026-03-24 to complete a ZooLATECH challenge. Be concise and practical.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774702800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774616555300,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 124001,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1774702800002\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ca097918-7155-44b5-80f9-4408f88c50ef\",\n